zh-tw.batch_add_domain_name_msg1: 以「Enter」鍵斷行可輸入多條域名，還可新增 {num} 筆

en.batch_add_domain_name_msg1: Press “Enter” key to create a new line and enter multiple domains. Still can add {num} domain(s).
en.batch_add_domain_name_msg2: The originally entered domains will be overwritten. Do you want to bulk add?
en.batch_add_placeholder_msg1: 1. Top-level domain and second-level domain have to be included, e.g., example.com.
en.batch_add_placeholder_msg2: 2. Only allow capital and small letter, numbers, “-“ and “.”.
en.batch_add_placeholder_msg3: 3. Each domain can only have 62 characters.
en.upload_file_add_domain_name_msg1: Please upload a .csv file. Up to {num} domains can be added.
en.upload_file_add_domain_name_msg2: The originally entered domains will be overwritten. Do you want to upload?
en.error_over_limit: It cannot be exported because exceeds the upper limit.
